{"tid":2492970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解大陸咁憎英國政府俾居英權香港人?","createTime":"2021-04-17T13:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T13:49:12.000Z","uid":128514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"552133c560c4fa392795fb892ce76a20ea7e39e9","tid":2492970,"uid":128514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"當年六四之後，英國政府推出5萬個居英權名額俾合資格香港家庭<br />\n中共反對<br />\n到今日英國政府設立BNO Visa 5+1俾香港人移民去佢到<br />\n中共又反對<br />\n<br />\n其實點解大陸咁憎英國俾居英權香港人?<br />\n如果我係中共的話，我會好開心，因為反對我既人將會走晒，剩低既人都係支持及擁護我國政府，更加可以考慮輸出優秀專才去香港，加強中港融合<br />\n我覺得係一件好事"},{"pid":"2cf0b3e4a46660e8bdd7f7f594cb63a723b404cb","tid":2492970,"uid":211466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"香港人唔聽話，走晒咪好囉<br />\n唔知佢嘈乜9"},{"pid":"a922417cc2119b205e4d8fa776377f61871bc268","tid":2492970,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c98a09174d07f708b4061d8f5c182a4215f2d39","tid":2492970,"uid":25601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2cf0b3e4a46660e8bdd7f7f594cb63a723b404cb","tid":2492970,"uid":211466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"香港人唔聽話，走晒咪好囉<br />\n唔知佢嘈乜9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"未就係 又話留地不留人 拎錢走佬都唔俾"},{"pid":"63c457c45e2691681f979c45f43f5a5807bbb988","tid":2492970,"uid":16719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"如果英國淨係俾元朗人Bc,隔離屯門都嬲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6918bd15c509eed215719255091182d86cb80cb5","tid":2492970,"uid":128514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a922417cc2119b205e4d8fa776377f61871bc268","tid":2492970,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji